Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:13.47,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Water collects into stagnant pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:18.43,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved watching it spill out all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:23.62,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking free, liberated, rushing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:28.60,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The energy stored up during \Nits stagnation bursts forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:32.46,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Everything springs into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:12.72,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki Mari-san, it's already noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:15.76,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I... I had the scariest dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:16.83,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:21.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed you put a wet towel on \Nmy face in an attempt to kill me, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:23.41,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}does{\i0} sound scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:25.98,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I told you yesterday to tidy up your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:28.48,sign_2077_12_Do_not_open_with,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Do not open\Nwithout permission!\N-Rin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:28.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:34.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
