Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.50,Ep_Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,One Mwillion Yen For Youth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.50,sign_5371_26_3_Likes_1_Commen,sign,0000,0000,0000,,3 Likes\N1 Comment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.50,sign_5371_27__OneMillionYen__,sign,0000,0000,0000,,#OneMwillionYen #Tanuki #Youth #Antarctica
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.33,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:56.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just realized, I'm in my second year \Nof high school and I haven't done {\i1}anything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.69,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything in \Nmiddle school either, Kimari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.59,sign_5748_32_Student_Activiti,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1500)}Student Activities
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I knew I had to start doing stuff \Nwhen I got into high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That it isn't good sleepwalking through life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,sign_5850_42_Youth_Doesn_t_Co,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Youth\NDoesn't\NCome to\NThose\NWho Wait
