Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,sign_5850_40_You_Can_Do_It_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,You Can\NDo It!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,sign_5850_41_Courage__Enthusi,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Courage,\NEnthusiasm,\NEnergy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I only have so much time, so I'm wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.03,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,where did all that determination go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.98,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.73,sign_6057_48_Get_the_most_out,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Get the most out of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,sign_6108_49_Expressions_to_o,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Expressions to offer advice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,sign_6108_50__Why_don_t_you__,sign,0000,0000,0000,,(Why don't you ____)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.73,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:22.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. First I'll go to Tokyo, \Nthen I'll start my journey from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Drifting from place to place on a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:24.82,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:25.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.07,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.36,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:31.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm g-gonna ditch school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.01,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm skipping school, though! Playing hooky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.80,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and it's not that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Not that big a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.69,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kimari... have you never ditched before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:44.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you have, Megu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.34,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I have. Everyone has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.10,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So, ever gone on a journey without a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.12,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then... then... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.01,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know that's what I meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:01.92,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,It was obvious. \NThat's just the way you think, Kimari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.90,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,But it's meaningless, unless you \Ngo by yourself, in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.26,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.99,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.37,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.58,sign_7525_79_Tamaki,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.58,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.25,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,So excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.57,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I'll get changed in \Nthe bathroom at the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.21,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.58,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.84,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. They'll know I'm from Gunma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.51,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.48,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Heading out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.27,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big bag for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I had to borrow gym clothes from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.63,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.95,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.33,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.16,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I had to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:06.34,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry. \NI already called the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.18,Italics,meg,0000,0000,0000,,With my mimicry skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.61,Italics,meg,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to stay overnight, \NI'll back up whatever story you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.68,Italics,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.31,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.19,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.89,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change clothes in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.65,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get on a train that goes \Nthe opposite direction from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.14,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,While everyone goes to school like normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.57,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I alone will burst free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.70,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on a journey without a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,To a place I've never seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.22,pants,sign,0000,0000,0000,,No loose pants!\NLift them higher! \NBoth your pants and your grades!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.35,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I mean, it was raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.25,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And I started thinking, \N"you can't just skip school"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.92,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anywhere you wanted to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, there is! Lots of places!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.51,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto, Okinawa, Hokkaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.60,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.56,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A plane could crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A shinkansen could explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.52,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,And a meteor could fall at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I know that! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.02,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.01,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You got scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.31,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You know. It's the thing I've always done...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:47.07,sign_10965_124_Rin,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,When I try to join clubs, \Nwhen I try to learn new things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,when I thought about taking the entrance \Nexam for a really good school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:47.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I always chicken out at the very last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm about to try something \NI've never done before,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I start thinking, \N"What if it doesn't go well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"I really don't want to fail."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"What if I end up regretting it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.95,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,When the moment comes, every single time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.41,sign_11535_133_Rin,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.41,sign_11535_134_Hurry_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.41,sign_11535_135_Want_to_eeeat,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Want to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:08.54,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think that's \Nnecessarily a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:17.68,sign_11795_138_I_ll_be_back_by_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back by curfew
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:17.68,sign_11795_139_I_made_the_usual,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I made the usual
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.90,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate that part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.53,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.54,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, want to hang out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.64,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dropped this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:30.79,sign_13536_146_Yen,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.97,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.45,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,How much is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.22,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I counted... it was exactly one million!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.72,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,A million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.46,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep it? Why didn't \Nyou take it to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.24,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I freaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.56,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.89,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious! I seriously freaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.92,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,And I think... the person who dropped \Nit was wearing a uniform for our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:55.74,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,What year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.14,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.86,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I only caught a glimpse of her from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.46,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,See her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.00,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.78,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Her hair was about as long as that \Ngirl's, and I think she was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.50,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.47,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,She smelled good. Conditioner, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:15.71,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Not much to go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.24,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.97,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there are many \Ngirls with hair that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.34,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check the first-year classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:23.85,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:31.86,sign_15054_170_Ethics,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ethics
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.86,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I need to calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.36,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,That smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,A million...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,A million... yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.95,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,A million...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.43,sign_16913_175_Open_and_close_d,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Open and\Nclose doors
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.43,sign_16913_176_QUIETLY,sign,0000,0000,0000,,QUIETLY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.43,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.94,sign_17082_178_Year_1_Class_1,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Year 1 Class 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.64,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.25,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Yesterday, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.67,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't steal it! I just happened to—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.73,sign_18109_188_Closed,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(693,1)}Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:43.53,sign_18168_190_A_Place_Further_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Place Further Than\N{\c&HF1F0E4&}the Universe\N{\fs14}Kobuchizawa Takako
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:43.53,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.68,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,My mother wrote this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She was a member of an \NAntarctic research expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She went missing when \NI was in middle school, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.96,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They never found her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.11,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,and she didn't leave much behind for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.09,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to go and find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,To Antarctica? \NCan you even do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's what everyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.05,sign_18787_200_Year_2_Class_2__,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Year 2 Class 2  We're All In This Together
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.05,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma, my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.48,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,my teachers, my upperclassmen, \Nand my neighbors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.56,sign_18931_204_New_Club_Formati,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Club Formation Application\NClub Name: Antarctica Club\NPrimary Purpose: To go to Antarctica\NClub Activity Details: Train and study to go to Antarctica. Go to Antarctica.\NMember names: President: 2-2 Kobuchizawa Shirase  Vice President: 2-2 Kobuchizawa Shirase\N(Must have 4)  2-2 Kobuchizawa Shirase  2-2 Kobuchizawa Shirase
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.68,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"You really think they'll \Nlet a child do that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't you realize how much that would cost?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what the million was for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.40,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working part-time jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:29.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, then rub it in the faces \Nof everyone who said I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:32.77,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,After I finished my entrance exams and \Ngot into high school, I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica, she said! Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.76,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.90,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The furthest ends of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.86,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That will be 566 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.52,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa Shirase?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You know her, Megu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.46,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,The girl in class 2 who they \Ncall "Antarctica," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.02,sign_20117_220_Coming_Nationwid,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Coming Nationwide This Winter!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.02,sign_20117_221_Anniversary_Coll,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Anniversary Collaboration Campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.96,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty famous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.33,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she got to high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:11.09,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,she's talked about nothing \Nbut going to Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.47,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.74,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she's going, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.05,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,But she has a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.96,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,And she said she was totally going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.29,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,She can't, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.21,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.74,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You'd need to be part of an expedition to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.18,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.42,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.45,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that's why people call her a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.00,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:35.14,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,She spends all her time after school \Nworking and saving up money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.85,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hang out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:49.40,Main,kim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:56.58,sign_21451_240_A_Place_Further_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}A Place Further Than\Nthe Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:57.97,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:28.11,sign_22068_242_300_Social_Scien,sign,0000,0000,0000,,300\NSocial Sciences
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:28.11,sign_22068_243_400_Natural_Scie,sign,0000,0000,0000,,400 Natural Sciences\N410 Math\N420 Physics\N430 Science\N440 Astronomy\N450 Earth Science\N460 Biochemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.78,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, that's my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.05,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.96,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Antarctic Express?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:49.84,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Where's our payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.05,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,We were making sure no one stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.03,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,We hear you've got some money on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.31,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend us a little? Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:16.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kobuchizawa-san, the teacher's calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.33,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They gotta ask some \Nquestions about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.87,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Way to spoil the fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You were lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the teacher really \Nfound out about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.96,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I gave you a knowing look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.35,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How was I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.41,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But why were you there? \NJust happened to be passing by?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:46.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I happened to see you, \Nand I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:48.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.86,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I want to encourage you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:59.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do something \Nwhen I got into high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:03.22,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Something I'd never done. Something amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I never did anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,and whenever I try, \NI end up getting scared and quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.64,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So... I think it's really amazing \Nto work hard at something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,even when everyone discourages \Nyou and makes fun of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:29.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Just let people say what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to show them up \Njust fires me up even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way I can help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.18,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Just say the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.15,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go with me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.88,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,People have said that to me in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But they all go away before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.68,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They decide it's impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.37,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,their friends get them to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.61,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Or they get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.15,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We're in high school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They have classes to get to, and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:23.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like them! My feelings \Nabout this aren't that frivolous...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.74,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm checking out boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.45,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Come here this Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll believe you're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.68,sign_26738_289_Antarctic_survey,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctic survey ship coming to Kure Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.68,sign_26738_290_Icebreaker_Shira,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Icebreaker Shirase Public Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:41.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"Icebreaker {\i1}Shirase{\i0}, public exhibition"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:47.06,sign_26941_292_Kawaraishi_Stati,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaraishi Station
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:47.06,sign_26941_293_Please_use_publi,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Please use public\Ntransportation to arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:47.06,sign_26941_294_Venue__Tsukijich,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Venue:\NTsukijicho, Kure, Hiroshima Prefecture \NKawaraishi South Pier, Kure Port
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.06,sign_27023_295_Hiroshima_Prefec,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshima\NPrefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.29,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Or they get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.72,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.92,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she's going, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.38,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go with me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.80,sign_27704_301_Icebreaker_Shira,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Icebreaker Shirase Public Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.80,sign_27704_302_A_Place_Further_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Place Further Than\Nthe Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.90,Main,sis,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.48,Main,sis,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's Saturday, \Nbut you can't sleep in forev—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.15,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:46.23,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I {\i0}am{\i1} going on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.99,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get on the train that goes \Nopposite the usual way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.21,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,so that I can see things \NI've never seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.83,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared; it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.31,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I want to call it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.10,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It might all turn out to be pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:21.99,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.29,sign_30544_313_I_m_finally_goin,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally going on a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.05,sign_30697_314_I_got_a_picture_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I got a picture of Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:42.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:44.42,sign_32618_315_Shirase,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:45.40,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Crossing the equator,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:47.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,weathering storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:49.64,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,breaking through ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:53.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,14,000 kilometers from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.99,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,To that place further than \Nthe reaches of the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.44,sign_33026_321_Passed_55_Degree,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Passed {\c&H251464&}55 {\c&H15347E&}Degrees South!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.44,sign_33026_322_12_December_2015,sign,0000,0000,0000,,12 December 2015, 12:27:58
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:23:01.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,that unapproachable place...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:09.45,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:14.45,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The corners of her mouth \Ncurled up in a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:21.46,sign_33476_328_Get_the_most_out,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Get the most out of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:20.97,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,My youth sprang into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:27.34,sign_33602_331_The_Place_Furthe,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2062)}The Place Further Than the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.87,0:23:40.75,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Miyake-san, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:42.04,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
